       lines  and  columns  (the full graphics frame), all categories from the
       map's color table will be displayed. However, if the user requests that
       the  color  table associated with a map which has 10 data categories be
       displayed in a graphics frame with only 3 lines (rows) and 2 columns (a
       total  of  six  cells), only six of the ten map categories will be dis-
       played.


